Convenience functions for calling geo()

Source: R/geo_methods.R
geo_census.Rd

The method for geo() is specified in the function name.

Use the geo function directly instead.

geo_census(...)

geo_osm(...)

geo_geocodio(...)

geo_iq(...)

geo_google(...)

geo_opencage(...)

geo_mapbox(...)

geo_here(...)

geo_tomtom(...)

geo_mapquest(...)

geo_bing(...)

geo_arcgis(...)

geo_cascade(...)

Arguments

...

arguments to be passed to the geo function
